data.title: Star Soldier: Vanishing Earth (Video Game 1998)
data.meta_description: Star Soldier: Vanishing Earth: In the year 2098, the dreaded Duoss Core has rebooted to lead the forces of planet Zeograd against mankind. Only the three F-98 Star Soldiers can save the Solar system.
